Global Aircraft Engine MRO Market Insights
Aircraft Engine MRO Market size was valued at USD 30.45 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 44.69 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Aircraft Engine MRO Market Overview
The global Aircraft Engine MRO (Maintenance, Repair, and Overhaul) market size was valued at USD 74.35 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 104.02 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.1% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for air travel, the rise in the global fleet of commercial and military aircraft, and advancements in engine technologies. The market is further supported by the expanding aviation industry, where aircraft maintenance plays a crucial role in enhancing engine performance, ensuring safety, and reducing operational costs.

